<div id="about" class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-sky-700 shadow-xl lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-4">
      <div class="px-6 pt-10 pb-12 sm:px-16 sm:pt-16 lg:py-16 lg:pr-0 xl:py-20 xl:px-20">
        <div class="lg:self-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">
            <span class="block">Our criteria</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-6 text-sky-100">Our investment criteria generally include the following:</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-md ml-5 leading-6 text-sky-300">Durable earnings with a proven track record of at least five years</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-md ml-5 leading-6 text-sky-300">Annual cash flow between $500,000 and $2,000,000</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-md ml-5 leading-6 text-sky-300">Existing management in place capable of continuing the business after sale</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-md ml-5 leading-6 text-sky-300">A business that is not excessively exposed to technological disruption</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-md ml-5 leading-6 text-sky-300">A business in an industry we can understand (the most limiting factor of all)</p>
          <p class="mt-10 text-lg leading-6 text-sky-100">Even if your business is not a good fit for us as owners, we will be delighted to work with you to find a buyer, arrange financing, restructure debt or even work through generational transition issues.</p>
          <a href="/financing" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-white px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-sky-600 shadow hover:bg-sky-50">Read about financing options</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-w-5 aspect-h-3 -mt-6 md:aspect-w-2 md:aspect-h-1">
        <Image
          src={featuredImage}
          class="translate-x-6 translate-y-6 transform rounded-md object-cover object-left-top sm:translate-x-16 lg:translate-y-20"
          alt="Stock charts"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
